title: MagicPrefs.app
description:
The best app. to enhance Apple Magic Mouse tracking speed (up to 200%) which was bothering me because before I started using this app. it was too slow.
Offers possibilities to increase ALL the Magic Mouse features and change some.
This version is for UP TO OSX 10.6.8. and it's actually free.
For more visit https://www.macupdate.com/app/mac/33095/magicprefs where I got it or the developer's site: http://magicprefs.com/

ENJOY!
